To build the package from scratch:

* Install utilities
 su -c "yum install rpmdevtools @development-tools"
* Setup rpm build tree
 rpmdev-setuptree
* Put spec-file in ~/rpmbuild/SPECS/
* Download sources to ~/rpmbuild/SOURCES/ using get_sources script.
* Install dependencies
 su -c "yum-builddep ~/rpmbuild/lxpanelx.spec"
* Build
 rpmbuild -ba ~/rpmbuild/SPECS/lxpanelx.spec